caption: Jack and Jack make me feel better about myself every single day and I'm so happy that they are together. I can't thank them enough for how much they've helped me even during the darkest times in my life. Literally when everything was terrible and I wanted to give up Jack and Jack both followed me that same day on Twitter which made me feel so much better I can't even explain it. I'm so proud of everything they've been doing and can't wait until I hear their songs on the radio like "Happy" except it will never be annoying. I love them so much #contest #contest #contest #contest
